window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>How did Lev Calder move from an unwillingly escaped Tithe to a clapper? In this revealing short story, Neal Shusterman opens a window on Lev’s adventures between the time he left CyFi and showed up at the Graveyard. Pulling elements from Neal Shusterman’s critically acclaimed <i>Unwind</i> and giving hints about what is to come in the riveting sequel, <i>UnWholly</i>, this short story is not to be missed.</p>"; 
